name: IYO-CHAN
description: IYO-CHAN ($IYO) is the enchanting ERC-20 meme token on Ethereum, born from the heartwarming tale of a real-life rescue dog.It was reclaimed by a passionate community, transforming from a feral underdog into a mythic mascot of resilience, loyalty, and unyielding bullish energy. Community-driven and unstoppable, $IYO channels the spirit of adoption into viral episodes, emblem evolutions, and meme magnetism that pulls holders into an ascending pride rock of positivity.
